<item>
            <title>[DERBY-2102] JDBC.assertFullResultSet should handle byte arrays</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2102</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, JDBC.assertFullResultset() cannot be used for columns that maps to byte[] (e.g., CHAR FOR BIT DATA).&lt;br/&gt;
To support this, assertRowInResultSet need to be extended the case where the column object is a byte[].&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
